      • getPlayerWithJersey

        private BasketballPlayer getPlayerWithJersey​(int jersey)
        This is a method that returns a BasketballPlayer when given a jersey number. It will look through the list of all players to see if one matches the given jersey number.
        Parameters:
        jersey - Parameter that takes an int that can be used for searching for a specified jersey number.
        Returns:
        Will return with a Basketball Player or null if a Basketball player with a matching jersey is not found.
